{"tid":2093364,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"鄧炳強今日生日","createTime":"2020-07-03T18:58:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T21:35:44.000Z","uid":160051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e263cb606c6c6430e73deede4b286c55202b9f8e","tid":2093364,"uid":160051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T18:58:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%2584%25A7%25E7%2582%25B3%25E5%25BC%25B7&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IKbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=2d1b57a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7</a><br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強，PDSM（英語：Chris Tang Ping-keung，1965年7月4日－），香港警務人員，現任香港警務處處長[2]，警隊中的鷹派人物，曾於中國人民公安大學、中國浦東幹部學院、國家行政學院及海外受訓。"},{"pid":"95d6d1d40a6ee35427554a6665c5db15105b864e","tid":2093364,"uid":191453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T19:00:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jCD5TWi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjCD5TWi.jpg&h=0823c6c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c49258a31ea8cca786961a816dbf4fcccf3fb58","tid":2093364,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T19:00:31.000Z","msg":"［多國文宣calling］<br />\n<br />\n其實對於我們的處境，我想這幾個國家會特別有體會：<br />\n<br />\n芬蘭（冬季戰爭）<br />\n捷克（布拉格之春，連儂牆，天鵝絨）<br />\n斯洛伐克。（同上，以前一個國家）<br />\n波羅的海三國（立陶宛，拉脫維亞，愛沙尼亞）（人鍊奇蹟）<br />\n越南 （打10年仗）<br />\n<br />\n本應有德國（柏林牆）<br />\n但德法宜家似乎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以色列應該WFC<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n應該嘗試大家一齊做多國文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就做左喇<br />\n你呢？<br />\n<br />\n或許還有：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俄羅斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[shocking<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n捷克文<br />\n香港連儂牆失敗了我們要怎麼辦<br />\nCo dělat, když selže Lennonova zeď v Hongkongu<br />\n<br />\n芬蘭文<br />\n我們需要曼那海姆構築我們的港人治港<br />\nTarvitsemme Mannaheimia autonomian rakentamiseksi<br />\n<br />\n愛沙尼亞文<br />\n現在人鏈被禁止了，絕望，怎麼辦<br />\nN&uuml;&uuml;d on inimkett keelatud, meeleheitel, mida ma peaksin tegema?<br />\n<br />\n大家補充！！！<br />\n和twitter plssssss"},{"pid":"ab99306f4f4b5f3f9a7a5b36a940b5de20958409","tid":2093364,"uid":150992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T19:03:46.000Z","msg":"屌狗"},{"pid":"d57ac9fe0fe89dc81a86ccb28a4c1fa22eb04c04","tid":2093364,"uid":344058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T19:06:30.000Z","msg":"有請燒山祝福下 thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ea80bcc37afda10a2541d689b8718cb5737c9e","tid":2093364,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T19:25:43.000Z","msg":"竟然係美帝國國慶生日"},{"pid":"c47aac9a03b11f2783284dd9aeddbc7540363e32","tid":2093364,"uid":239336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T19:30:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vwQDuES.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvwQDuES.gif&h=77c53700&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29aac3d76fc1778016e04fbf5148866de2da5b2a","tid":2093364,"uid":359029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T20:20:21.000Z","msg":"Pk, 年年冇今日；腦中風死"},{"pid":"96b2e050a164d7ddedb3a26a8670f90e89c3231f","tid":2093364,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T21:32:50.000Z","msg":"早登地獄 善哉善哉"},{"pid":"6f9f99850bfa7524345898d12ed0e9d4ec246f21","tid":2093364,"uid":230293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T21:35:44.000Z","msg":"大家係想要邊種民主？<br />\n<a href=